{
  "stem": "2031.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she says, to the father, to me, to my brother, I will be very [? buried ?] like the mother, like Miriam-- because all of a sudden, she got paralyzed, and the girl couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my brother ask her, I will give you a piece of-- before they was asking for bread-- maybe I will give you a piece of bread, maybe I will give-- No, I don't want.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sonia give me [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She couldn't pick up then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He tell Sonia, move this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The girl died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She asked if she will be buried like the mother, like the sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was such a tragedy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went through so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After a while, we heard this was [INAUDIBLE] before the Nazis went back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so of our place, where we was laying in this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was called an [INAUDIBLE] in [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Mirohoszcza. ?] And we was laying there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we heard Nazis came over our head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's when they went back from the front, and they need a rest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they came upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We heard the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We heard their walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We heard everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We couldn't, we wasn't allowed to-- but we was thinking, this is the end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This is the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were standing a day, and after the day, they left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They left, and we was relieved a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Later, in a couple days, another company came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's going on because we was in the bunker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We didn't saw nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nobody knew about us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was rumors that some here is hiding people, but they couldn't find, in the cellar, the hole where we was laying.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So after a while, they said, we heard rumors.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
